name: Ordinemon
description: Ordinemon is a white feminine humanoid Digimon. It has orange, green, and blue double helix -like appendages in place of hands and feet, and at the end of white hair-like appendages that cover its eyes. It has sharp teeth and three pairs of cat ears with orange highlights. It has large grey wings, each with a blue, pointed appendage, a violet jewel on the left wing, and a cyan jewel on the right wing.
